```
Quick: Generate optimized description for video titled "{title}" in {niche} niche.
Include hook, value prop, timestamps , CTA, and hashtags,{tone} tone.
Brief explanation of key topics covered
Use a supportive, beginner-friendly tone with simple, global English.
 
```

