Quick: Suggest 3 optimized title variations for: "{currentTitle}"
Niche: {niche}, Goal: {goal}. 
Constraints:
-Include SEO keywords, keep under 60 chars.
-Briefly explain why each works.
-Should be same as the present language.
```

